verbose_text: MDA-MB-231 control cells and MDA-MB-231 cells stably expressing HSV1-sr39TK, NTR, and HSV1-sr39TK-NTR fusion proteins induced 5.54, 34.6, 8.19, and 40.2% of cell death, respectively, 3 days post-treatment and 14, 70.3, 18.7, and 88% cell death 5 days post-treatment.
